\section{Introduction}
   In recent years, the hypothosis that human released carbon dioxide will warm planet earth has become an huge issue. There is naturally a
large body of work in it. However very few of the calculation tools for the issue are released as open source. In this work we present
a program and it results to numerical integrate carbon dioxide and water vapour absorption over frequency, latitude and height, producing a percentage
absorbtion ammount for the two green house gases.

